-- Lloyds remains confident of paying 2014 dividend
-- 
-- Tue Oct 28, 2014 03:40AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Oct 28 (Reuters) - Lloyds Banking Group <LLOY.L> remains hopeful of paying a dividend for 2014 despite only achieving a narrow pass in a stress test by European regulators, Finance Director George Culmer told reporters on a conference call.

